Titolo: Bite the Bullet (video game)

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Bite the Bullet is an RPG roguelite shooter developed by Mega Cat Studios. It was released for Microsoft Windows and Nintendo Switch on August 13, 2020, Xbox One on August 14, 2020, and PlayStation 4 on February 24, 2021. The game is a run, gun, and eat, and features arcade-inspired run and gun action combined with various eating mechanics. Bite the Bullet received mixed reviews from critics.